    "Initially, a microscope was used to identify cells that were contaminated with malaria.",
    "Due to the sheer volume of data to analyse and the complexity of the timing, it could result in false diagnosis.",
    "Increasing time requirements and inaccurate diagnosis have led to a significant need for autonomous parasite diagnosis methods.",
    "For the purpose of identifying the malaria parasite, a smart mathematical framework is developed.",
    "As extracting features strategies, biochemical, physiochemical, and Computational Linguistic (CL) approaches are employed."
